  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\nThe Pending Requests counter is shown not in the full size - the top part of it appears partially\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. User A blocked and unblocked User B\r\n2. User B sent a Contact Request to User A\r\n3. User A went to Settings -> Messaging -> Contacts -> Pending\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe counter is shown correctly\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nThe counters looks incorrect - the top part is cropped\r\n### Additional Information\r\n<img width=\"1287\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/14942081/171075349-ba9a2552-8b89-482b-b5b1-a5b5cc3a8fc9.png\">\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: [Build #2137 (May 30, 2022, 9:02:25 AM)](https://ci.status.im/job/status-desktop/job/branches/job/macos/job/master/2137/)\r\n- Operating System: macOS Monterey 12.3 Beta (21E5227a) M1\r\n\r\n",
